Subject: Filesystem Scans not working
Description: When starting a scan it gives me the following error: Stealthbits.StealthAUDIT.DataCollectors.FSAA.FSAAException: Unable to start scan: Could not initialize scan session with any proxy host supplied at Stealthbits.StealthAUDIT.DataCollectors.FSAA.AccessScanTask.InternalProcessRecord() at Stealthbits.StealthAUDIT.DataCollectors.Tasks.Task.StartExecute() I've updated the Netwrix Auditor and the Filesystem Proxy, since we had the a different message regarding Access Violation, which was mentioned in the patch notes.
Solution_Comment__c: Customer had a version mismatch between proxy server and NEA. They were updated and then certificates were deleted using KB https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/z-kb-articles-salesforce/page/kA0Qk0000000WSvKAM.html. Issue is resolved.
